To generate the patch file do the following:
git diff > canvas.diff

then move the canvas.diff file to your dwm folder and run
patch -F3 -i canvas.diff

recompile dwm (don't forget to cat config.def.h > config.h) and it should work fine.

go see:
https://codeberg.org/wh1tepearl/vxwm

for more details.
